            "id": "gt0001",
            "text": "MAP calculation",
            "description": "Calculates an approximated Mean Arterial Pressure (MAP). MAP is defined as the average pressure in patient's arteries during one cardiac cycle.\n\nNote, true MAP can be determined by invasive monitoring and other calculation methods."
